^ M. Kobayashi, T. Maskawa. CP-Violation in the Renormalizable Theory of Weak Interaction. Progress of Theoretical Physics. 1973, 49 (2): 652–657. Bibcode:1973PThPh..49..652K. doi:10.1143/PTP.49.652. 
^ The Nobel Prize in Physics 1980. NobelPrize.org. Nobel Media. [17 March 2011]. 
^ Paul Langacker. Cp Violation and Cosmology. (編) Cecilia Jarlskog. CP violation. London, River Edge]: World Scientific Publishing Co. 1989, 2001: 552.  請檢查|date=中的日期值 (幫助)
^ 24.0 24.1 K. Nakamura et al. (Particle Data Group). Gauge and Higgs Bosons (PDF). Journal of Physics G. 2010, 37. 
^ K. Nakamura et al. (Particle Data Group). n (PDF). Journal of Physics G. 2010, 37: 7. 
^ S.L. Glashow. Partial-symmetries of weak interactions. Nuclear Physics. 1961, 22: 579. doi:10.1016/0029-5582(61)90469-2. 
